# Agent skills installed via the skills CLI. The manifest skills-lock.json IS committed
# (reproducible source of truth); the installed content (.agents/, ~2MB of third-party
# skills from vercel-labs / Panniantong) and the .claude/skills/* symlinks that point into
# it are the node_modules-equivalent — rebuild them by re-running the installer, never vendor.
.agents/
.claude/skills/agent-reach
.claude/skills/deploy-to-vercel
.claude/skills/vercel-cli-with-tokens
.claude/skills/vercel-composition-patterns
.claude/skills/vercel-optimize
.claude/skills/vercel-react-best-practices
.claude/skills/vercel-react-native-skills
.claude/skills/vercel-react-view-transitions
.claude/skills/web-design-guidelines
.claude/skills/writing-guidelines
# Images are local-only by default (bucket map + retention:
# docs/conventions/workspace-hygiene.md). design-reference/ is re-included below.
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.webp
# macOS / iCloud Drive sync conflict-copies. The repo lives under an iCloud-synced
# ~/Documents path, so concurrent writes by parallel tools (Claude Code · Lovable ·
# Gemini · Antigravity) make iCloud spawn numbered duplicates like
# "feature-dashboard 2.md" or "src/components 2/". Never commit them — the canonical
# file is the unsuffixed one. Durable fix: move the repo off the iCloud-synced path.
* [0-9].*
* [0-9]
* [0-9]/

# Local screenshots / visual artifacts (organized under docs/screenshots, kept local).
# Where each image goes + retention: docs/conventions/workspace-hygiene.md
docs/screenshots/

# Exception: canonical design-reference images ARE committed (file-placement
# policy — docs/README.md §"Where everything lives"). The global *.png/*.jpeg
# ignores above keep verification/QA captures local; these re-include only the
# curated references a parallel build (Lovable · Gemini · Antigravity · Claude
# Code) must match — one canonical image per screen, never a bulk dump.
!design-reference/**/*.png
!design-reference/**/*.jpeg
!design-reference/**/*.jpg
!design-reference/**/*.gif
!design-reference/**/*.webp

# Served social/preview image (the cosmic brand-band OG card) must be committed so it
# deploys and link previews work.
!public/og-cadence.png
